<div class="container">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Help Section</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the Pahana Edu Billing System Help Section.</p>
        <h3>How to Use the System</h3>
        <ul style="list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li><strong>Login:</strong> Use your username and password to access the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Add Customer:</strong> Navigate to "Add New Customer" to enter customer details (auto-generated account number, first name, last name, address, telephone).</li>
            <li><strong>Edit Customer:</strong> Select a customer from "Display Accounts" to update their information.</li>
            <li><strong>Manage Items:</strong> Add, edit, or delete book items under "Manage Items". Include item name, unit price, and stock quantity.</li>
            <li><strong>Display Accounts:</strong> View all customer accounts and their details.</li>
            <li><strong>Calculate Bill:</strong> Select a customer, choose multiple items, specify quantities, and generate a bill. The system automatically reduces item stock.</li>
            <li><strong>Print Bill:</strong> View and print the itemized bill with customer and item details.</li>
            <li><strong>Logout:</strong> Click "Logout" to exit the system securely.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>